<abstract><t>The BGP Remote-Next-Hop is a new optional transitive attribute intended to facilitate automatic tunneling within an AS on a per address family basis.  The attribute carries one or more tunnel end- points for a NLRI.  Additionally tunnel encapsulation information is communicated to successfully setup these tunnels.</t></abstract>

